  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The objective of this study is to review studies and patient symptoms before and after
      laparoscopic Heller myotomy to assess outcomes following laparoscopic surgery for achalasia.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Patients will answer questionnaires before and after surgery to evaluate their symptoms of
      achalasia and will also have their charts reviewed for relevant medical information.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
